<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.4.9">
<l>pūṇit toḻuviṉiṟ pukkup puḻuti yaḷaintapoṉ mēṉi</l>
<l>kāṇap peritu mukappa ṉākiluṅ kaṇṭār paḻippar</l>
<l>nāṇet taṉaiyu milātāy nappiṉṉai kāṇiṟ cirikkum</l>
<l>māṇkka mēyeṉ maṇiyē mañcaṉa māṭanī vārāy</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I am very happy to see your golden body</l>
<l>after having entered the cattle stall and wallowing in dust,</l>
<l>even if whoever [else] sees you will ridicule [you].</l>
<l>You have no shame at all!</l>
<l>If Nappiṉṉai sees [you], she will laugh.</l>
<l>Ruby! My Jewel! Come take your ceremonial bath!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
